::Proto/Grimmler/Firearm::

Proto and Grimmler emerge from the Cybertronian Fire, opening fire on Dracona 
and Twister.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm comes to a stop near a door, frowning. The control panel near it 
showed that it was locked. He pushes a few buttons, activating a view of the 
interior. A female was inside, wearing Predacon simbles. Firearm frowns. 
Tapping a few buttons, he unlocks the door, setting his arm cannon for rapid 
fire just in case. He takes a few steps forward, the door opening, Firearm's 
cannon ready...
